son\\\": \\\"hadoop-yarn-server-common:2.9.0 declares hadoop-common as provided, but its public and implementation APIs reference org.apache.hadoop.conf.Configuration, security token/protobuf classes, RPC annotations, and HTTP filter interfaces needed for realistic YARN server-common coverage.\\\"\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"agent_guidance\\\": \\\"No Docker service appears necessary for meaningful tests. Prefer in-process coverage of YARN PB records, BuilderUtils, security/filter initialization with Configuration(false), shared-cache utilities, and the in-memory federation store/policy classes. Avoid SQLFederationStateStore and ZookeeperFederationStateStore unless the test explicitly configures embedded/test infrastructure.\\\",\\n  \\\"risks\\\": [\\n    \\\"If the workflow copies the existing 2.8.2 test scaffold, this dependency may already be present and should not be duplicated.\\\",\\n    \\\"Exercising SQL or ZooKeeper federation stores would require additional test infrastructure, but those paths are not necessary for baseline meaningful coverage.\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\",\"textSignature\":\"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0570a188c4e4e5cf016a3e4f0249a08195a69fe7cea8248b4e\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"}],\"api\":\"openai-responses\",\"provider\":\"OCA\",\"model\":\"oca/gpt-5.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":3073,\"output\":1335,\"cacheRead\":30720,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":35128,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1782468330851,\"responseId\":\"resp_0570a188c4e4e5cf016a3e4eeb55f481958057e3fa08ec3208\"}}\n=== /home/vjovanov/.pi/agent/sessions/--home-vjovanov-c-forge-forge2-graalvm-reachability-metadata-forge-local_repositories-forge_worktrees-8597-18f1886d--/2026-06-26T10-07-14-898Z_019f0365-dbd2-749c-af85-9b65cd13483b.jsonl ===\n{\"type\":\"session\",\"version\":3,\"id\":\"019f0365-dbd2-749c-af85-9b65cd13483b\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-26T10:07:14.898Z\",\"cwd\":\"/home/vjovanov/